{
  "stem": "3933.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Always in Christmas time, the-- Poland is 99%-- 98% Catholic.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Always then, before-- shortly-- shortly before Christmas Eve, we have to avoid them, not to go out in the evenings.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Many times they were-- little pogroms.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Ooh.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There was not, in the history of Poland, a policeman, a Jewish policeman, even a mail deliverer.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Not in the history of Poland.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They were representing the-- the same, the parliament.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "There was representative, naturally, we are citizens.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You heard about her?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I took the book in the library.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I read a lot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was-- her story when she went to Poland to find about the Jewish organizations.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She wrote-- Anyway, there's a-- Is John Jewish?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because I don't want that story.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's the reason I ask.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, it's just recently.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then there is a part where it's something very new to me. 3 and 1/2 million Jews were in Poland.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Poland was already making up things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There's already-- Poland started to make pact with a certain nation, a certain nation-- Madagascar-- I didn't even know-- to chase out 3 million Jews from your country.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just like that, you chase out all the Jews from America.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Born there.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Several generations born.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I couldn't believe my ears.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I-- I mean, I said, Mary, you are not naive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You come from there, from this anti-Semitic-- but to just like that, to chase out your citizens.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then my son came shortly after that, and I said to him, oh, Eric.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Among other things, my son speaks fluently Polish [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He has a little sentiment for them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't know why.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then he said, oh, Mama.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is the word he said to me, and I'm still angry.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Oh mama, really.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That would be a historic-- what are you talking about mama?",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
